sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as TrainJob Controller<br/>trainer-controller-manager
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller<br/>v0.10.1
    participant Scheduler as Volcano Scheduler<br/>Gang Scheduling
    participant Pods as Training Pods<br/>GPU workloads
    participant Storage as S3/HuggingFace<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    %% Flow 1: TrainJob Creation
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation
        User->>API: kubectl apply TrainJob<br/>Auth: User credentials
        API->>Webhook: Validate TrainJob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
        Webhook-->>API: Validation response
        API->>Controller: Watch event (CREATE)<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>API: Create JobSet<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
        Controller->>API: Create PodGroup (gang scheduling)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
        Controller->>API: Create NetworkPolicy (RHOAI)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    end

    %% Flow 2: Training Execution
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over JobSetCtrl,Storage: Flow 2: Training Execution
        JobSetCtrl->>Scheduler: Schedule training pods<br/>PodGroup all-or-nothing
        Scheduler->>Pods: Create pods (node-0, node-1...)<br/>GPU allocation
        Pods->>Storage: Download dataset/model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>AWS IAM auth
        Storage-->>Pods: Model artifacts
        Pods->>Pods: Inter-pod communication<br/>Dynamic TCP<br/>NCCL all-reduce, MPI, gRPC
        Note over Pods: Distributed training<br/>torchrun, DeepSpeed, MPI
    end

    %% Flow 3: Progression Tracking (RHOAI)
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Controller,Pods: Flow 3: Progression Tracking (RHOAI)
        loop Every 30s (configurable)
            Controller->>API: List training pods<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
            API-->>Controller: Pod IPs
            Controller->>Pods: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP<br/>NetworkPolicy restricted
            Pods-->>Controller: JSON metrics<br/>{progressPercentage, loss, step}
            Controller->>API: Update TrainJob annotation<br/>trainer.opendatahub.io/trainerStatus
        end
    end

    %% Flow 4: Gang Scheduling Detail
    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Controller,Scheduler: Flow 4: Gang Scheduling (Volcano)
        Controller->>API: Create PodGroup<br/>scheduling.volcano.sh
        Scheduler->>API: Watch PodGroup<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
        Note over Scheduler: Wait until all pods ready<br/>All-or-nothing scheduling
        Scheduler->>Pods: Schedule all pods simultaneously<br/>Prevent deadlock
    end
